# Secret environment for the basic-delivery example.
#
# Copy to `secrets/.env` (gitignored) only when Smith or another configured
# responder needs environment variables. Temper does not read provider auth files
# or provider secrets; it only allow-lists names for the responder process.
#
# Example: if SMITH_WORKFLOW_ROLE_DECISION_ARGS_JSON in config/temper.env selects
# a Smith mode that reads a provider variable, set the secret here and add the
# variable name to SMITH_WORKFLOW_ROLE_DECISION_ENV_ALLOWLIST.
#
# SMITH_PROVIDER_SECRET=...
# TEMPER_DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=...
#
# Forgejo admin tokens are minted by the launcher for the provision step and are
# not pasted here.
#
# TEMPER_FORGEJO_ADMIN_TOKEN=
